casebody.data:
PEOPLE
v.
WATTS S246063 Supreme Court of California February 21, 2018 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

The petition for review is granted. The matter is transferred to the Court of Appeal, Second Appellate District, Division One, with directions to vacate its decision and reconsider the cause in light of S.B. 620 (Stats. 2017, ch. 682). ( Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(d).)
